wiki.content:
"Disco Inferno" is the first single from 50 Cent's second album, The Massacre. Released in December 2004, the single peaked at number three in the U.S. becoming 50 Cent's fifth top ten single. The song was produced by C. Styles & Bang Out. The song was nominated for Best Rap Solo Performance at the Grammy Awards of 2006.
